<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Đừng để t gặp lại m 😡- Password Reset</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #FAFAFA; color: #222222;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="background-color: #C8A846; padding: 24px; color: #ffffff; text-align: center;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0;">Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your LunarStore's account.</p>
            <p>Please use the following code to reset your password:</p>
            <h2 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; color: #0070f3;">{{resetCode}}</h2>
            <p>This code is valid for the next 10 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact us for support.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/phat.thinhvinh.7/" target="_blank" style="color: #0070f3; text-decoration: none;">
                    Thình Vĩnh Phát</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>